    <item>
      <title>美国机场获得近 10 亿美元联邦资金用于改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/us-airports-get-nearly-1-billion-in-federal-funds-for-makeovers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超过 100 个美国机场将获得 9.7 亿美元的联邦拨款，这是升级国家基础设施的最新举措——乔·拜登总统的首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/us-airports-get-nearly-1-billion-in-federal-funds-for-makeovers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普再次出庭纽约法院，三起案件的关键判决相互冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/trump-in-ny-court-again-as-key-decisions-in-three-cases-collide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四在曼哈顿一家法院出庭受审，指控他涉嫌向一名色情明星支付封口费，与此同时，针对这位前总统的至少三起备受关注的案件出现了重大进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/trump-in-ny-court-again-as-key-decisions-in-three-cases-collide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普拉博沃阵营誓言选举获胜后组建包容性联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/prabowo-camp-vows-inclusive-coalition-after-indonesia-vote-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位竞选官员表示，普拉博沃·苏比安托在周三的总统选举中取得令人信服的胜利后，将跨越党派界限，试图组建一个稳定的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/prabowo-camp-vows-inclusive-coalition-after-indonesia-vote-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 07:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最高法院在政党资助案中裁定莫迪败诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/india-s-supreme-court-bans-political-funding-via-electoral-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院驳回了由总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府牵头的一项不透明的政治融资工具，这是距离选举仅几个月就做出的令人惊讶的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/india-s-supreme-court-bans-political-funding-via-electoral-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:37:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京介入美国竞选，支持“旧式”拜登而非特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/putin-says-predictable-biden-better-for-russia-than-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京称赞乔·拜登是俄罗斯比唐纳德·特朗普更可靠的选择，这是他首次对美国总统选举发表公开评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/putin-says-predictable-biden-better-for-russia-than-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳因债务谈判和选举临近而更换财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/ghanaian-president-removes-ofori-atta-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳总统纳纳·阿库福-阿多 (Nana Akufo-Addo) 更换了财政部长，因为这个西非国家希望在 12 月选举之前与商业债权人就债务重组达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/ghanaian-president-removes-ofori-atta-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
